trans-unit.source: Provides a serializable type of endpoint address that is compliant with the version of WS-Addressing published in August 2004 and that enables it to be exposed as part of the service contract.
trans-unit.target: Inneholder en serialiserbar type Endepunktadressen som er kompatibel med versjonen av WS-adressering publisert i August 2004 og som gjør det mulig å vises som en del av servicekontrakten.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.ServiceModel.EndpointAddress> is not serializable nor is it tied to a particular version of the WS-Addressing specification.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.ServiceModel.EndpointAddress>er serialiserbare eller knyttet til en bestemt versjon av WS-adressering-spesifikasjonen.</xref:System.ServiceModel.EndpointAddress>

trans-unit.source: [!INCLUDE[indigo1](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] supplies a class that provides a serializable type, <xref:System.ServiceModel.EndpointAddress10>, which is WS-Addressing V1 compliant.
trans-unit.target: [!INCLUDE[indigo1](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)]angir en klasse som gir en serialiserbar type <xref:System.ServiceModel.EndpointAddress10>, som er WS-adressering V1 samsvar.</xref:System.ServiceModel.EndpointAddress10>

trans-unit.source: This class provides a WS-Addressing August 2004 compliant wrapper for the <xref:System.ServiceModel.EndpointAddress> that is serializable and bound to a particular wire format for legacy purposes.
trans-unit.target: Denne klassen gir WS-adressering August 2004 kompatible wrapper for den <xref:System.ServiceModel.EndpointAddress>som er serialiserbare og bundet til en bestemt wire-formatet for eldre formål.</xref:System.ServiceModel.EndpointAddress>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.ServiceModel.EndpointAddressAugust2004.FromEndpointAddress%28System.ServiceModel.EndpointAddress%29> method does the wrapping and the <xref:System.ServiceModel.EndpointAddressAugust2004.ToEndpointAddress%2A> method does the unwrapping, allowing the recovery of the endpoint address after being serialized on the wire.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.ServiceModel.EndpointAddressAugust2004.FromEndpointAddress%28System.ServiceModel.EndpointAddress%29>metoden har wrapping og <xref:System.ServiceModel.EndpointAddressAugust2004.ToEndpointAddress%2A>metoden har den unwrapping, slik at gjenoppretting av Endepunktsadressen etter som serialiseres på nettet.</xref:System.ServiceModel.EndpointAddressAugust2004.ToEndpointAddress%2A> </xref:System.ServiceModel.EndpointAddressAugust2004.FromEndpointAddress%28System.ServiceModel.EndpointAddress%29>

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.ServiceModel.EndpointAddress10"></xref> class with a specified endpoint address.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.ServiceModel.EndpointAddress10"> </xref> klassen med en angitt Endepunktadressen.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.ServiceModel.EndpointAddress> is not tied to a particular version of the WS-Addressing specification or bound to a particular wire format.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref:System.ServiceModel.EndpointAddress>er ikke knyttet til en bestemt versjon av WS-adressering-spesifikasjonen eller bundet til en bestemt wire-formatet.</xref:System.ServiceModel.EndpointAddress>

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.ServiceModel.EndpointAddress> used to initialize the instance of this class.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.ServiceModel.EndpointAddress>Brukes til å starte forekomsten av denne klassen.</xref:System.ServiceModel.EndpointAddress>

trans-unit.source: The <xref href="System.ServiceModel.EndpointAddressAugust2004"></xref> class that contains the specified endpoint address.
trans-unit.target: Den <xref href="System.ServiceModel.EndpointAddressAugust2004"> </xref> klassen som inneholder at Endepunktadressen som er angitt.

trans-unit.source: Returns an XML-qualified name that describes the XML representation of the version 1 endpoint address from a specified cached schema.
trans-unit.target: Returnerer en XML-kvalifisert navn som beskriver XML-representasjon av versjon 1 Endepunktsadressen fra et angitt bufrede skjema.

trans-unit.source: This method is required by the serialization contract.
trans-unit.target: Denne metoden kreves av serialisering kontrakten.

trans-unit.source: It must be public to be seen by the XmlSerializer.
trans-unit.target: Det må være felles å vises av XmlSerializer.

trans-unit.source: It is not intended to be called by developers.
trans-unit.target: Det skal ikke kalles av utviklere.

trans-unit.source: A <xref:System.Xml.Schema.XmlSchema> that contains a cache of the XML schema definition language (XSD) schemas for the endpoint address.
trans-unit.target: En <xref:System.Xml.Schema.XmlSchema>som inneholder en hurtigbuffer for XML-skjema definition language (XSD) skjemaer for Endepunktsadressen.</xref:System.Xml.Schema.XmlSchema>

trans-unit.source: A <xref:System.Xml.XmlQualifiedName> that describes the XML representation of the endpoint address.
trans-unit.target: En <xref:System.Xml.XmlQualifiedName>som beskriver XML-representasjon av Endepunktsadressen.</xref:System.Xml.XmlQualifiedName>
